<ab>Cristoff von <expan>Layming<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu Lawff </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst bevor. <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan>, als wir ewch nehst
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Wynm<ex>er</ex></expan> zu ewch gesandt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        von der nom und <expan>beschedigu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die ir ettwievil
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lewte<ex>n</ex></expan> zu <expan>Newkirche<ex>n</ex></expan> getan
                        habt, also sind die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> für uns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                        klagen ir und der iren scheden swerlich; <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        ewch, daz ir den <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>arme<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lewte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> ir hab und das ir in kürcz keret und
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> schaffet und uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> sache fürbas
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>traget</expan>, das steet uns umb ewch zu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schulden</expan>; wan gescheͣh des niht, so
                        meynen die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, daz in das von ewch kein gefallen
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, wan wir noch die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> des kriegs niht zu schiken haben.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
